d to classify\nvariables into different variability classes in an automated, unsupervised way,\na feature that has immense potential for larger databases of the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Mar 2009 11:54:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Jul 2009 12:40:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 11 Sep 2009 12:12:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
